                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Comme un invalide sur un banc.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "La Luxure me dit à l’oreille :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Bonhomme, on vous a déjà donné.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3−6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Et l’Orgueil se tait comme un damné.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est Paris banal, maussade et blanc,\nQui chantonne une ariette vieille\nEn cuvant sa « noce » de la veille\nComme un invalide sur un banc.\nLa Luxure me dit à l’oreille :\nBonhomme, on vous a déjà donné.\nEt l’Orgueil se tait comme un damné."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "O Jésus, vous voyez que la porte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Est fermée.au Devoir qui frappait,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Et que l’on s’écarte à mon aspect.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
